Class HamCycStateSmp

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.pj2.Tuple
      • edu.rit.pj2.example.HamCycState
        • edu.rit.pj2.example.HamCycStateSmp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Streamable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class HamCycStateSmp
extends HamCycState
    Class HamCycStateSmp encapsulates the state of a search for a Hamiltonian cycle in a graph in a multicore parallel program. Class HamCycStateSmp supports both breadth first search (BFS) and depth first search (DFS).
